OL,3,CClosure of 'essential' waste facility
OL,4,Cfor boaters on Kennet and Avon Canal
OL,6,FThe closure of a "essential" waste
OL,7,Ffacility for boaters near Bath was
OL,8,Fordered by the local council, canal
OL,9,Fbosses have said.
OL,11,FBathampton boaters were shocked when
OL,12,Ftheir bin facility, which had been a
OL,13,Fhotspot for fly tipping, was closed
OL,14,Fdown at short notice on 11 March.
OL,16,FA petition against the move, which has
OL,17,Fbeen signed by over 450 people,
OL,18,Fquestioned why the Canal and River
OL,19,FTrust could not simply have put a lock
OL,20,Fon the facility or increased its
OL,21,Fsecurity.
OL,26,@nD@ROUnD@\O]
