OL,6,FThe trust has said it had tried to
OL,7,Fimprove security but was blocked by
OL,8,FBath and North East Somerset Council
OL,9,Fand told to remove the bins.
OL,11,FMark Evans, regional director at the
OL,12,FCanal & River Trust said: "We are
OL,13,Fdisappointed that we've had to close
OL,14,Fthe bin store at Bathampton.
OL,16,F"This was after the council rejected
OL,17,Four proposal to invest in improving
OL,18,Fthe security of the compound and
OL,19,Fthreatened enforcement action. It was
OL,20,Fon their instruction that the site had
OL,21,Fto be closed.
