OL,6,F"Frustratingly, the fly tipping at the
OL,7,Fbin store, which costs our charity
OL,8,Fmany thousands of pounds, isn't
OL,9,Fthought to be from boaters ` who,
OL,10,Falong with residents, colleagues and
OL,11,Fcontractors have all been helping to
OL,12,Ftry to manage and rectify the
OL,13,Fsituation.
OL,15,F"The trust and the council had
OL,16,Fpresented a united front to upset
OL,17,Fboaters last week, saying in a joint
OL,18,Fstatement that they were working
OL,19,Ftogether to resolve the issue."
OL,26,@nD@AOUwD@AO]
