OL,6,FBut council leader Kevin Guy, who is
OL,7,Falso the local councillor for Bathavon
OL,8,FNorth, said in his capacity as local
OL,9,Fcouncillor that the trust had "failed
OL,10,Fboth the Bathampton and boater
OL,11,Fcommunities."
OL,13,FResponding, Mr Evans said: "We have
OL,14,Fbeen working with the council in good
OL,15,Ffaith, so the incorrect statements
OL,16,Fmade by the leader of the council are
OL,17,Fvery frustrating.
OL,26,@qD@_OUsD@MO]uD@\OU
