OL,4,Cfor boaters on Kennet and Avon Canal
OL,6,F"We urge them to agree to a delay in
OL,7,Fthe closure of the site, which is on
OL,8,Fcouncil owned land, whilst we work
OL,9,Ftogether to identify a way forward.
OL,11,F"Whilst our preference is to invest in
OL,12,Fimproving the site, we will also seek
OL,13,Fto identify nearby alternative sites
OL,14,Fthat could serve our customers, albeit
OL,15,Fwith some added inconvenience."
