OL,3,CClosure of 'essential' waste facility
OL,4,Cfor boaters on Kennet and Avon Canal
OL,6,F"However, given the case history of
OL,7,Fthis waste facility, the council's
OL,8,Fwaste services have entirely lost
OL,9,Ffaith in the ability of the CRT to
OL,10,Fmanage this or any other new facility
OL,11,Fat this location.
OL,13,F"There is no evidence to suggest that
OL,14,Fthe CRT have the capability to manage
OL,15,Fany new store at this location in a
OL,16,Fmanner which would address the issues
OL,17,Fof overflowing bins, large scale rat
OL,18,Finfestation and fly tipping."
