OL,3,CClosure of 'essential' waste facility
OL,4,Cfor boaters on Kennet and Avon Canal
OL,6,FBoaters ` many of whom bid higher
OL,7,Fprices for moorings near to the
OL,8,Ffacility ` now face having to make
OL,9,Flong trips to dispose of their rubbish.
OL,11,FThe next closest bins on the canal are
OL,12,Fin Bath or at the Dundas basin, but
OL,13,Fboaters have warned they are already
OL,14,Ftoo full and too far to travel to with
OL,15,Frubbish.
OL,17,FAnother nearby facility in Darlington
OL,18,FWharf was closed years ago.
OL,20,FCredit: John Wimperis, Local Democracy
OL,21,FReporting Service.
